description:
e o u i e, the legacy of a name. 
A rhythm of remaining vowels. 

Reused to create this brand. Young urban design for daily life pursuits. Inspired by time, led by need. 

Design, produce and distribute within the same borders. This aim is the basis for our future. 

High quality garments with minimum impact on human and nature. Made from remaining fabrics saved from death row. Reused to create this movement.
